name: Sensor Web Server Helgoland API v3.4.4
body:
Available in [Maven Central](https://search.maven.org/search?q=g:org.n52.sensorweb-server.helgoland%20and%20v:3.4.4).

## Change Log 
* None

## Dependency Updates
* Bump arctic-sea.version from 9.6.0 to 9.8.0 (#680, #686, #692)
* Bump tzinfo from 1.2.9 to 1.2.10 in /web-resources/src/main/docs (#681)
* Bump spring-boot-dependencies from 2.7.1 to 2.7.5 (#682, #687, #694, #697)
* Bump junit-bom from 5.8.2 to 5.9.1 (#683, #693)
* Bump geotools.version from 27.0 to 27.2 (#684, #698)
* Bump joda-time from 2.10.14 to 2.12.0 (#685, #688, #695, #696)
* Bump jackson-bom from 2.13.3 to 2.13.4 (#690)
* Bump spotbugs-annotations from 4.7.1 to 4.7.2 (#691)

## Breaking Changes
* None

See [here](https://github.com/52North/sensorweb-server-helgoland/compare/v3.4.3...v3.4.4) for the complete commit log.
